      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.9SpVyycUKIvoDFJb]{Silent Slayer}</p>\n<p>Your unexpected attacks leave targets devastated and erratic. When you hit an opponent with a melee attack who was not aware of your presence, it is @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.DtwiUWi8dpzkq4tM]{Frightened} for 1d4 rounds. If you score a critical hit, the target is instead @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.BVdjvpucmvQU4cc1]{Panicked} for 1d4 rounds. The target can attempt a Will saving throw at the end of each round to remove the frightened or panicked condition (DC = 10 + half your soldier level + your key ability modifier).</p>"
